(62, 31, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544462415-5c4e1062755a?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=M3w3NTg5MjV8MHwxfHJhbmRvbXx8fHx8fHx8fDE3NDg5NTIxNDN8&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&q=80&w=1080', '<p>Records are making a comeback. There are so many styles you could try to capture in a record store, but rarely does a record have on it “the one and only” to describe an artist. Not just any artist too, the one and only Glenn Miller.</p>\n<p>Photo by Mick Haupt on Unsplash</p>'),
